Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.recnplay.Event

  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which will be instantiated into specific instance and will be stored in game history for future replay use such as Move object which is created in Application module.
